  "title": "Gently Wrapped Korean Pak Choi Ssam Wrap",
  "description": "A kid-friendly Korean dish featuring pak choi and ssam wrap, served in a terracotta dish, with a nutty and chewy texture, and macrobiotic-friendly ingredients.",
