  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "Cut the pak choi into small pieces and set aside.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the sesame oil, soy sauce, garlic, and ginger.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the ssam wrap pieces.",
    "Place a small amount of brown rice onto each ssam wrap piece.",
    "Add a few pieces of pak choi on top of the rice.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds and salt over the pak choi.",
    "Gently wrap each ssam wrap piece into a bundle.",
    "Place the bundles into a terracotta dish and bake for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy."
  ],
